{
  "stem": "14168.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And all I can tell you is they say it was a heart attack.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Well, to say the least, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it was completely incomprehensible to me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "As we found out later, my father had been asked to present himself to the police.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My [? mother-- ?] he-- when he came home, my mother said, the police have been here.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They want you.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He said, well, I have not done anything criminal.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I'm not worried about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So he went to the police.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He thought-- he believed in law and order.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That was the mentality of a lot of German Jews.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We haven't done anything, so what can they do to us?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The police sent him to the gathering station-- the depot in Breslau where he was shipped to-- from where he was shipped, with hundreds of others, to Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Buchenwald, they killed him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I have eyewitnesses who live in the United States who were present.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] He collapsed, and so they killed him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And a few days later, my mother, who didn't know where he was, was summoned to the Gestapo-- Gestapo headquarters.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they said, we have to tell you, as a matter of factly, that your husband died of a heart attack.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then they gave her a cigar box.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They said, here's is-- here are his ashes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when my mother cried out, they said, look.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You're taking-- you're-- you're robbing us of our time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Don't carry on here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, they came.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They just wanted to know where my father was and where I was.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They said to my mother, unless they present themselves immediately, we'll ransack the whole place.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They didn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
